{"word":"ἁμαρτία","slug":"ἁμαρτία","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἁμαρτία, ας, ἡ</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἁμαρτάνω\">ἁμαρτάνω</a></el>; ‘a missing of the mark’]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘misdeed that creates liability for the agent’, <b><i>sin:</i></b><i></i> <b><a href='B:470 9:2'>Mt 9:2</a>; <a href='B:500 8:46'>J 8:46</a>; <a href='B:660 5:15'>Js 5:15</a>; <a href='B:690 5:16'>1 J 5:16b</a></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ al.\">al.</a> <el>προσφορὰ περὶ ἁ.</el> = <i>sin-offering</i> <b><a href='B:650 10:18'>Hb 10:18</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘the condition of being sinful’, <b><i>sinfulness</i> <a href='B:500 9:41'>J 9:41</a>; <a href='B:500 19:11'>19:11</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>3.</pp></b> ‘an invasive evil power’<b> <a href='B:520 5:12'>Ro 5:12</a></b> and often; <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <b><a href='B:650 3:13'>Hb 3:13</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἁμάρτημα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἁμάρτυρος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}